            "creation_date": 1540273025,
            "body": "<p>I have a simple solution for your problem. When user selects all, then in that case pass the empty list and while making the query just put this condition.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>if (outletList.size()==0) {\n// case for all\n} else {\n// do regular stuff\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 52941806,
            "question_id": 52941675
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/XR9JP.png?s=256",
                "account_id": 1441892,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 1361787,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1361787/chieftwopencils",
